20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20around%20us.%26quot%3B%20This%20makes%20it%20slower%20and%20harder%20for%20people%20to%20switch%20over%20to%20smart%20glasses%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20that%20will%20take%20a%20longer%20journey.%20The%20good%20news%20is%20they%20work%20really%20well%20in%20concerts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBosworth%20praised%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-vision-pro-mixed-reality-headset-specs-cost-release-date-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple's%20Vision%20Pro%20headset%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20his%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%2C%20but%20said%20the%20company%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Brookie%20mistake%26quot%3B%20when%20they%20made%20the%20device%20too%20heavy%20to%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20from%20an%20engineering%20standpoint%2C%20it's%20wonderful%20and%20congratulations%20to%20that%20team.%20From%20a%20product%20standpoint%2C%20you%20can%20tell%20it's%20their%20first%20offering%20in%20the%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20generation%20products%20are%20hard.%20It's%20not%20until%20the%20second%20or%20third%20generation%20that%20you%20really%20figure%20out%20and%20hone%20the%20thing%2C%20and%20they%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20mistakes%20in%20that%20in%20terms%20of%20weight%20and%20where%20the%20weight%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBosworth%20isn't%20the%20only%20Meta%20executive%20who%20thinks%20smartphones%20won't%20be%20displaced%20by%20smart%20glasses.%20The%20social%20media%20giant's%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20podcast%20with%20The%20Verge%20in%20September%20that%20he%20didn't%20think%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20are%20getting%20rid%20of%20phones%20anytime%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20we're%20going%20to%20throw%20away%20ou