oopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F322864%2Fkochi-aathira-sethumadhavan-pcos-weight-loss-healthy-diet-nutrition-sustainable-lifestyle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanyone%20seeking%20a%20healthier%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20says.%20This%20feedback%20gave%20him%20the%20confidence%20to%20push%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jatin%20Sarin%2C%20a%20senior%20consultant%20in%20oncology%20based%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CCancer%20is%20increasingly%20recognised%20as%20a%20lifestyle%20disease%2C%20with%20poor%20dietary%20habits%20playing%20a%20major%20role.%20Our%20food%20today%20is%20often%20packed%20with%20chemicals%20and%20has%20fewer%20essential%20nutrients.%20Microgreens%2C%20however%2C%20are%20a%20different%20story.%20These%20young%20plants%2C%20which%20are%20harvested%20after%20the%20sprout%20stage%2C%20are%20packed%20with%20micronutrients%20and%20offer%20a%20wealth%20of%20health%20benefits.%20They%20can%20be%20a%20valuable%20addition%20to%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20diet%2C%20complementing%20conventional%20treatments%20like%20chemotherapy%20and%20radiotherapy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMicrogreens%20are%20rich%20in%20vitamins%2C%20minerals%2C%20and%20antioxidants%2C%20making%20them%20a%20great%20choice%20for%20anyone%20looking%20to%20boost%20their%20overall%20health%20and%20well-being.%20I%20have%20included%20them%20in%20my%20diet%20and%20have%20noticed%20an%20improvement%20in%20my%20energy%20levels%20and%20overall%20vitality.%20Their%20nutritional%20density%20makes%20them%20an%20ideal%20food%20for%20maintaining%20health%2C%20preventing%20illness%2C%20and%20promoting%20a%20healthier%20lifestyle%20for%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20oncologist%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kuldeep%20Singh%2C%20learning%20about%20microgreens%20farming%20proved%20to%20be%20beneficial%20for%20gaining%20profits.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20met%20Mohit%20at%20the%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%2