20microgreens%20farming%20lies%20in%20its%20simplicity%20and%20efficiency.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20venture%20by%20selecting%20high-quality%20and%20non%20genetically%20modified%20(non-GMO)%20seeds.%20I%20source%20mine%20from%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendras%20(KVK)%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20they%20are%20organic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mohit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20seeds%20are%20sown%20in%20sterilised%20growing%20media%2C%20like%20cocopeat%20or%20coco%20coir%2C%20in%20trays.%20The%20microgreens%20are%20watered%20with%20a%20minimal%20amount%20of%20just%2030%20ml%20of%20water%20per%20tray%20daily.%20He%20does%20not%20use%20any%20chemicals%20or%20pesticides%20in%20his%20farming%20and%20only%20believes%20in%20following%20organic%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20a%20considerable%20investment%20of%20around%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%20you%20can%20set%20up%20a%20small-scale%20microgreens%20operations%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886-768x402.j