process-gardening-tips-small-space-okra%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20A%20City%20Running%20Out%20of%20Green%2C%20This%20Vast%20Vikhroli%20Mangrove%20Has%20Protected%20Mumbai%20for%204%20Decades%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99ve%20ever%20driven%20from%20Mumbai%20towards%20Thane%20on%20the%20Eastern%20Express%20Highway%2C%20you%20might%20have%20felt%20a%20gradual%20dip%20in%20temperature%20of%20up%20to%20five%20degrees.%20As%20you%20pass%20Ghatkopar%20and%20approach%20Kanjurmarg%2C%20your%20windows%20fog%20up%20slightly%2C%20the%20air%20cools%2C%20and%20everything%20seems%20a%20little%20quieter.%20No%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20your%20imagination%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20mangroves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20your%20right%2C%20hidden%20behind%20the%20industrial%20facade%20of%20the%20city%2C%20lies%20one%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20best-kept%20secrets%3A%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F414695%2Fgorai-mangrove-park-in-mumbai-opening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esprawling%20mangrove%20forest%3C%2Fa%3E%20quietly%20flourishing%20within%20the%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pirojshanagar%20Township%20in%20Vikhroli.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpread%20over%20thousands%20of%20acres%2C%20this%20green%20lung%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20offering%20a%20cooler%20commute%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20regulating%20microclimates%2C%20filtering%20air%20and%20water%2C%20and%20shielding%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20eastern%20shoreline%20from%20floods%20and%20erosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20monsoon%2C%20rainfall%20in%20this%20pocket%20is%20often%20heavier%20and%20gentler%2C%20absorbed%20by%20the%20thirsty%20roots%20of%20the%20mangroves.%20The%20Creekside%20Colony%2C%20one%20of%20three%20residential%20clusters%20near%20the%20forest%2C%20enjoys%20what%20residents%20call%20a%20%E2%80%98good%E2%80%99%20climate%E2%80%99%E2%80%94cleaner%20air%2C%20less%20heat%2C%20and%20an%20occasional%20chorus%20of%20birdsong.%20All%20of%20this%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20city%20constantly%20battling%20rising%20temperatures%2C%20waterlogging%2C%20and%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20just%20one%20visible%20outcome%20of%20a%20much%20deeper%2C%20long-term%20commitment.%20Since%20they%20acquired%20the%20land%20in%20the%201940s%2C%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%20has%20chosen%20to%20preserve%20and%20protect%20this%20mangrove%20ecosystem%2C%20not%20as%20a%20CSR%20project%2C%20not%20for%20branding%2C%20and%20not%20as%20a%20compliance%20tick%20box%E2%80%94but%20as%20an%20act%20of%20belief%E2%80%94a%20belief%20that%20business%20and%20biodiversity%20can%20exist%20harmoniously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20even%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20concrete%20jungle%2C%20a%20forest%20can%20be%20nurtured%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20care%20enough%20to%20protect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20%E2%80%98wasteland%E2%80%99%20to%20ecological%20treasure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERewind%20to%20the%201940s%20%E2%80%94%20a%20time%20when%20mangroves%20were%20largely%20misunderstood.%20Often%20dismissed%20as%20marshy%20wastelands%20or%20potential%20real%20estate%2C%20they%20were%20left%20unprotected%2C%20encroached%20upon%2C%20and%20plundered%20for%20firewood%20by%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20late%20Sohrabji%20Godrej%2C%20a%20nature%20lover%20and%20industrialist%2C%20saw%20something%20others%20didn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ecosystem%20worth%20preserving.%20Under%20his%20guidance%2C%20Godrej%20initiated%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F260147%2Finitiative-saving-mumbai-mangorves-environment-godrej-and-boyce%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5