nservation%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tejashree%20Joshi%2C%20Head%20of%20Environmental%20Sustainability%20at%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20research%20uncovered%20not%20just%20which%20species%20lived%20here%2C%20but%20how%20they%20survived%2C%20coexisted%20or%20were%20at%20risk..%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%20when%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98mangrove%E2%80%99%20was%20confused%20with%20%E2%80%98mango%E2%80%99%2C%20this%20research%20provided%20the%20foundation%20and%20a%20science-backed%20roadmap%3A%20what%20to%20protect%2C%20where%20to%20intervene%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20why%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20an%20expert%20from%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20science%20rooted%20the%20forest%E2%80%99s%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20data%20and%20information%2C%20the%20Godrej%20team%20rolled%20out%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331813%2Fkochi-murukesan-plants-lakhs-of-mangrove-along-kerala-coastline-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree-pronged%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20model%20that%20still%20guides%20the%20initiative%20today%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EResearch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Baseline%20biodiversity%20studies%2C%20continuous%20ecological%20monitoring%2C%20species%20inventory%20updates.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EConservation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Securing%20the%20forest%2C%20replanting%20native%20mangroves%2C%20controlling%20access%2C%20and%20preventing%20exploitation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreating%20awareness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Educating%20employees%2C%20local%20communities%2C%20and%20schoolchildren%20through%20immersive%2C%20long-term%20engagement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20about%20ticking%20the%20Environmental%2C%20Social%2C%20and%20Governance%20(ESG)%20boxes%20%E2%80%94