3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20college%20fest%20idea%20into%20e-waste%20revolution%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENandan%E2%80%99s%20journey%20%E2%80%94%20from%20formulating%20the%20idea%20during%20his%20college%20days%20at%20St.%20Xavier%E2%80%99s%20to%20establishing%20a%20thriving%20e-waste%20management%20company%20%E2%80%94%20echoes%20the%20transformative%20influence%20of%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CHulladek%20started%20as%20a%20business%20plan%20I%20presented%20during%20a%20college%20fest%20at%20St.%20Xavier%E2%80%99s.%20I%20proposed%20a%20model%20for%20collecting%20and%20recycling%20electronic%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20it%20won%20me%20the%20competition%20and%20an%20internship%20at%20E-Parisaraa%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20e-waste%20recyclers.%20That%20experience%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20my%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENandan%20spent%20two%20years%20working%20with%20a%20waste%20management%20company%20in%20Bilbao%2C%20Spain%2C%20rotating%20through%20procurement%2C%20logistics%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20dismantling.%20That%20global%20exposure%20helped%20him%20build%20a%20solid%20foundation%20for%20Hulladek%20Recycling%20when%20he%20returned%20to%20India%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHulladek%20is%20a%20Hungarian%20word%20for%20%E2%80%98waste%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20universal%20nature%20of%20the%20problem%20we%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20solve.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20seen%20waste%20not%20as%20a%20burden%2C%20but%20as%20a%20resource.%20That%20mindset%2C%20alongside%20the%20growing%20urgency%20of%20climate%20action%20and%20sustainable%20industry%2C%20cemented%20my%20belief%20that%20waste%20