ycling-2-1748957868-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-443719%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHulladek%20Recycling%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20addressing%20the%20overlooked%20issue%20of%20e-waste%20in%20India%2C%20which%20contains%20valuable%20yet%20hazardous%20materials.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20while%20conversations%20around%20plastic%20and%20biodegradable%20waste%20are%20growing%20louder%2C%20e-waste%20barely%20makes%20a%20whisper.%20It%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20most%20dangerous%20pollutants%20of%20our%20time%2C%20and%20still%20one%20of%20the%20least%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20Hulladek%20comes%20in%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20as%20a%20recycling%20company%2C%20but%20as%20a%20changemaker.%20With%20a%20mission%20to%20spread%20awareness%2C%20build%20responsible%20collection%20systems%2C%20and%20recover%20resources%20without%20harming%20health%20or%20the%20environment%2C%20Hulladek%20is%20working%20to%20turn%20a%20crisis%20into%20an%20opportunity.%20They%E2%80%99re%20showing%20that%20what%20we%20throw%20away%20could%20actually%20be%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20cleaner%2C%20more%20sustainable%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20bins%20to%20businesses%3A%20revolutionising%20e-waste%20recycling%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%20Recycling%20works%20on%20two%20fronts%20%E2%80%94%20directly%20with%20everyday%20households%2C%20and%20in%20partnership%20with%20large%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdver