mpanies%20must%20ensure%20their%20e-waste%20is%20being%20collected%2C%20recycled%2C%20and%20disposed%20of%20safely%2C%20not%20just%20tossed%20aside.%20The%20law%20also%20sets%20clear%20targets%3A%20by%202023-24%20and%202024-25%2C%2060%25%20of%20e-waste%20generated%20must%20be%20recycled.%20That%20figure%20rises%20to%2070%25%20in%20the%20following%20two%20years%20and%20hits%2080%25%20from%202027-28%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%E2%80%99s%20work%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20both%20individuals%20and%20industries%20to%20meet%20these%20goals%2C%20not%20just%20on%20paper%2C%20but%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20operates%20with%20a%20dual%20approach%2C%20holding%20collection%20drives%20for%20households%20and%20managing%20e-waste%20for%20major%20corporations.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-3-1748957873-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-443720%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20operates%20with%20a%20dual%20approach%2C%20holding%20collection%20drives%20for%20households%20and%20managing%20e-waste%20for%20major%20corporations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20their%20operation%20model%2C%20Shreya%20Khandelia%2C%20the%20Executive%20Vice%20President%2C%20Recycler%20Relations%20of%20Hulladek%20Recycling%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20initial%20collection%20of%20e-waste%20from%20our%20dedicated%20centres%2C%20the%20materials%20are%20segregated%20and%20sent%20to%20authorised%20recyclers.%20Recycling%20involves%20dismantling%2C%20treating%20hazardous%20components%2C%20and%20segregating%20materials%20into%20categories%20like%20glass%2C%20metal%2C%20and%20plastic%20for%20reuse%20or%20upcycling.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20step%20is%20carefully%20monitored%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20environmental%20standards%2C%20a%20practice%20that%20distinguishes%20us%20from%20informal%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwala%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(scrap%20dealers)%2C%20who%20are%20often%20confused%20with%20formal%20recyclers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreya%20says%20what%20makes%20Hulladek%20unique%20is%20not%20just%20its%20mission%20but%20its%20workforce%2C%20which%20is%20predominantly%20led%20by%20women.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20an%20average%20employee%20age%20of%2027%2C%20we%20strive%20to%20be%20innovative%20in%20the%20waste%20management%20industry%2C%20and%20our%20gender%20diversity%20is%20unparalleled%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shreya%20beams%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20rooted%20in%20an%20apparent%20belief%3A%20change%20begins%20with%20awareness.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20built%20a%20formidable%20logistics%20network%20backed%20by%20intention%20and%20community%20engagement.%20With%20more%20than%2060%20collection%20centres%20spread%20across%20cities%20like%20Surat%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Agartala%2C%20Hulladek%20conducts%20over%20500%20awareness%20sessions%20each%20year%E2%80%94each%20one%20an%20attempt%20to%20shift%20mindsets%20and%20turn%20passi